{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c0ed05d05d","title":"关于批判《修养》的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0fa60e9ba0","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"c0ed05d05d"},{"id":"f111eded4b","index":1,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"c0ed05d05d"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"b89508bbcb","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"c0ed05d05d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指刘少奇的《论共产党员的修养》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4da37f6172","type":"title","text":"关于批判《修养》“的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"c0ed05d05d"},{"id":"b89508bbcb","type":"paragraph","text":"千万不要再上《修养》那本书的当。《修养》这本书，是欺人之谈，脱离现实的阶级斗争，脱离革命，脱离政治斗争，闭口不谈革命的根本问题是政权问题，闭口不谈无产阶级专政问题，宣扬唯心主义的修养论，转弯抹角地提倡资产阶级个人主义，提倡奴录主义，反对马克思列宁主义、毛泽东思想。按照这本书去“修养”，只能是越养越“修”，越修养越成为修正主义。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"c0ed05d05d"},{"id":"600f548f3b","type":"paragraph","text":"皖","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"c0ed05d05d"},{"id":"447603886a","type":"paragraph","text":"这本书完全是欺人之谈。革命的基本问题，就是政权问题。到底要不要夺取政权，能不能夺取政权，怎样夺取政权，对于这些基本问题，这个小册子（即《修养》）避而不谈。根本不谈夺取政权，不谈无产阶级专政，离开了政权，离开了阶级，离开了阶级分析，离开了阶级斗争，完全是一本资产阶级唯心主义的、反动的、不触及蒋介石一根毫毛的东西，是一株资产阶级的大毒草","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"c0ed05d05d"},{"id":"2247cdf774","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"c0ed05d05d"},{"id":"d6607d136a","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇的《论共产党员的修养》我看过几遍，这是反马列主义的。我看大学生应该更好地研究一下，选几段写文章批判。要批判刘少奇的《论共产党员的修养》和邓小平多年来的讲话。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"c0ed05d05d"},{"id":"7a420fb61b","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"c0ed05d05d"},{"id":"99c1d82d99","type":"paragraph","text":"我从来就不同意“聊服工具论”","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"c0ed05d05d"}],"page":{"id":"2b9216a303","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"c0ed05d05d","start":390,"end":391}}}},"__N_SSG":true}